title: BMW Car
paragrap: The story of the BMW 1602 Electric carries an inspiring message through time: Great change begins with a small step. This summer, the iconic vehicle celebrates its 50th birthday at the European Championships Munich 2022, marking the first step for the BMW Group into the world of e-mobility.
